adsb-history-logger (0.2.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix packaging: activate the debhelper python3 sequence so dh_python3
    actually runs. Without it, files installed to a build-machine-specific
    /usr/lib/python3.X/dist-packages path instead of the version-independent
    /usr/lib/python3/dist-packages, breaking the package on any target
    running a different Python 3 minor version than the CI runner.

 -- enbay1 <enbay1@gmail.com>  Tue, 21 Jul 2026 12:55:00 +0000

